112struct kafs_data;
113struct kafs_token;
114typedef int (*afslog_uid_func_t)(struct kafs_data *,
115 const char *,
116 const char *,
117 uid_t,
118 const char *);
119
120typedef int (*get_cred_func_t)(struct kafs_data*, const char*, const char*,
121 const char*, uid_t, struct kafs_token *);
122
123typedef char* (*get_realm_func_t)(struct kafs_data*, const char*);
124
125struct kafs_data {
126 const char *name;
127 afslog_uid_func_t afslog_uid;
128 get_cred_func_t get_cred;
129 get_realm_func_t get_realm;
130 const char *(*get_error)(struct kafs_data *, int);
131 void (*free_error)(struct kafs_data *, const char *);
132 void *data;
133};
134
135struct kafs_token {
136 struct ClearToken ct;
137 void *ticket;
138 size_t ticket_len;
139};
